## Examples

#### Covert a CSV document to a Turtle document
```js
@{cat('snippets/transform-csv.js')}
```

Run from the command line with:
```sh
cat <<EOF | node snippets/transform-csv.js
> 1,Blake,Banana
> 2,Banana,Water Sunlight Soil
> EOF
```

Outputs:
```turtle
@{exec('snippets/transform-csv.js', {
  input: [
    '1,Blake,Banana',
    '2,Banana,Water Sunlight Soil',
  ].join('\n'),
})}
```


